---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const lang = "en";
---

<Layout
  title="Support Pachatopia"
  description="Together, let's bring life back: tree planting, coffee tree sponsorship, natural reserve support, and partnerships."
  lang={lang}
>
  <Header lang={lang} />
  <main>
    <!-- Hero Banner -->
    <section class="relative text-white py-24 md:py-36 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0">
        <img src="/images/community.jpg" alt="Support Pachatopia" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" aria-hidden="true" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/80"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-heading font-bold mb-6">🌱 Support Pachatopia</h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90">Together, let's bring life back</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How you can help -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-cream">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-12">Pachatopia is an ecological and human regeneration project. By supporting our initiative, you participate in soil restoration, tree planting, and the development of nature-friendly agriculture. Every contribution, big or small, helps this vision grow.</p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-10">How you can help</h2>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <article class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">🌳 Plant trees</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Trees are at the heart of our project. They regenerate soils, promote biodiversity, and participate in ecosystem restoration.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">☕ Sponsor a coffee tree</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Our coffee is grown in an agroforestry system that protects biodiversity and improves soil fertility.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-3">Sponsoring a coffee tree helps support local farmers, restore soils, and develop sustainable agriculture.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">🌍 Support the natural reserve</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">A portion of the land is dedicated to nature protection and ecosystem regeneration. Your support helps preserve these spaces for future generations.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">🤝 Become a partner</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Businesses, organizations, or individuals can support Pachatopia by becoming project partners.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Coffee Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 space-y-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-primary">☕ Our coffee</h2>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-primary">A coffee that regenerates the Earth</h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Pachatopia coffee is grown at the heart of a living ecosystem. Rather than producing in intensive monocultures, we grow our coffee within a regenerative agroforestry system, surrounded by trees, plants, and biodiversity.</p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">This model helps regenerate soils, promote biodiversity, protect water, and support local communities. Every cup of coffee becomes a gesture for the Earth.</p>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-primary">A meaningful coffee</h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">When you choose Pachatopia coffee, you are not just supporting an agricultural product. You are participating in the restoration of living ecosystems, the rebuilding of a territory marked by history, and the promotion of nature-friendly agriculture.</p>

        <p class="text-lg text-primary font-semibold italic">Every cup of coffee is a seed planted for the future.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/en/le-cafe/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 bg-golden text-primary font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-golden-dark transition-colors">☕ Discover Pachatopia coffee</a>
          <a href="/en/comment-participer/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 border-2 border-primary text-primary font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">🌳 Sponsor a coffee tree</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Charter -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-cream">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-primary">🌿 The Pachatopia Charter</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">🌱 Regenerate the Earth</p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">🤝 Cultivate cooperation</p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">🕊 Work for peace</p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">🌍 Respect the living world</p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">🌳 Pass on to future generations</p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Pachatopia is a human and ecological adventure open to all. Every tree planted, every gesture of support, and every person involved helps this vision grow. Together, let's bring life back.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer lang={lang} />
</Layout>
